wpt.desc: TIRED of waiting! by C.A.P., Traditional Cache (1/1)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: TIRED of waiting!
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: Easy find, plenty of parking across the street. Great area! Almost a drive up and cache.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description: This is my second cache. It's a quick one, use caution for muggles, and when you are done stop by the bakery and grab a cupcake. They are amazing! It's is just feet off a paved sidewalk and could be seen from the sidewalk! Have fun searching and after this one and the cupcake, take a nice walk to Berwyn Memorial to get another cache! BYOP. Can hold small items.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:encoded_hints: Watch out for emergency vehicles and mechanics.

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: This one took some looking. I was ready to DNF it, but my daughters persisted and made the find.
